{"tid":2366721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大學生向公司舉報她母親支持川普 導致她母親被解僱","createTime":"2021-01-14T18:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T20:18:12.000Z","uid":225931,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"030a76788ac9ca3e5458f701b1e2ca5bdb8a7905","tid":2366721,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T18:12:09.000Z","msg":"一名美國大學生向她母親的公司舉報她母親支持川普，導致她母親被解僱，全家人生活陷入困境，她也交不起學費了，她在網上展開眾籌。有人說美國也出現總加速師了，帶領全社會踩油門左轉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/help-helena-duke-pay-for-college\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fhelp-helena-duke-pay-for-college&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=eceafaa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/help-helena-duke-pay-for-college</a><br />\n<br />\nAs you may know from recent twitter and news sources I have called out my mother for her actions. At the moment I have no idea how I will be paying for college as I have little financial support. I have a dream of one day becoming a lawyer but I need help to get there. I hope to attend college and then go into the peace corps. Eventually I hope to enter into law school. I want to make the world a better place I just need some help"},{"pid":"9a3495b8c6fe75b936e2bd23f5431dcfc6a0a06e","tid":2366721,"uid":17510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T18:13:41.000Z","msg":"真係支那式批鬥<br />\n<br />\n香港又係咁  黃？！即炒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唉"},{"pid":"04ecb1e84097022b7ccd2486836dea3525157da6","tid":2366721,"uid":20241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T18:16:47.000Z","msg":"等啲左膠都享受下文化大革命"},{"pid":"c6ae2e49f623a717b5199de7ecf56bc2dbfe230a","tid":2366721,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T18:18:39.000Z","msg":"超光速主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass